            <font color="blue" size="6">Comparing methods of extracting objects from images</font>
        </div>
</center>
<div>
    <font size="4"><p>Extracting an object from an image is an important task for many photographers and artists.   As shown below, the person in the left image was separated from the background as shown in the right image.</p></font>

<div id="images">
    <a >
        <img src="intro_pics/im.png" alt="Image" style="height:500px;">
